br />\n彭耀霆:建中科學班<br />\n陳煜中:中一中科學班<br />\n沈江宥:附中科學班<br />\n林峻丞:IJSO銀, 保送雄中科學班<br />\n馬宇辰:國八AMC10滿分<br />\n賴政瑋:附中科學班<br />\nAnd more…</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:24px;\">詳見以下臉書連結：</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/XCunQKUTcfs4tJny/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">https://www.facebook.com/share/p/XCunQKUTcfs4tJny/</a></span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
